&lt;p&gt;This AGU Fall Meeting 2024 presentation reports whole-rock elemental and
Sr-Nd-Pb isotope constraints on sediment recycling at the Makran arc. The work
connects geochemical systematics with sediment inputs and arc volcanic outputs.&lt;/p&gt;
